      transliteration: "yasminnidaṁ vicikitsanti mṛtyo\nyatsāmparāye mahati brūhi nastat\nyo'yaṁ varo gūḍhamanupraviṣṭo\nnānyaṁ tasmānnaciketā vṛṇīte",
