      transliteration: "anyacchreyo'nyadutaiva preya-\nste ubhe nānārthe puruṣam̐ sinītaḥ\ntayoḥ śreya ādadānasya sādhu\nbhavati hīyate'rthādya u preyo vṛṇīte",
